<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Repayment Interest</title>

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        font-family: "Mulish", sans-serif;
      }
      @media (max-width: 425px) {
        .content {
          padding: 0 23px;
          margin: 38px 0;
        }
        .content h2 {
          font-size: 22px;
        }
        .content p {
          font-size: 12px;
        }
        .main-btn {
          margin-top: 40px;
          font-size: 18px;
        }
        .disclaimer {
          padding: 24px;
        }
        .footer {
          padding: 34px 24px;
        }
        .footer-wrap {
          padding: 27px 24px;
        }
        .download-row-desktop {
          display: none !important;
        }
        .download-row-mobile {
          display: table-row !important;
        }
      }
      @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .download-buttons {
          display: grid;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <table
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      border="0"
      style="margin: 40px 0"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <img
            src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Email%20Assets/ekuid-logo.png"
            alt="Ekuid"
            width="100"
            border="0"
            style="display: block"
          />
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <main class="container" style="padding: 0">
      <img
        src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Email%20Assets/repayment-interest.png"
        alt="Repayment Interest"
        class="main-image"
        style="width: 100%"
      />

      <section class="content" style="padding: 0 30px; margin: 48px 0">
        <h2
          style="
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif;
            color: #243962;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 100%;
          "
        >
          Hai <%= firstName %>,
        </h2>
        <p
          style="
            margin: 0;
            margin-top: 24px;
            color: #69758b;
            font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 150%;
            letter-spacing: 0.238px;
          "
        >
          Terima kasih telah mempercayai EKUID untuk berinvestasi!<br /><br />

          Selamat! Pada hari ini, <b><%= currentDate %></b>, Penerbit
          <b><%= projectName %></b> telah melakukan pembayaran imbal hasil
          dengan detail sebagai berikut:<br /><br />

          Nominal Pembayaran Imbal Hasil: <b><%= repaymentAmount %></b><br />
          Pembayaran Imbal Hasil ke: <b><%= numberOfRepayment %></b><br /><br />

          Silakan cek status berkala imbal hasil kamu melalui rekening yang
          terdaftar ya! Jika ada pertanyaan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi tim
          kami melalui tombol WhatsApp di bawah, ya!
        </p>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 42px; text-align: center">
          <!-- Secondary button -->
          <a
            target="_blank"
            href="https://wa.me/6281213137125?text=Hai Rico, saya membutuhkan bantuan di"
            style="text-decoration: none"
          >
            <button
              style="
                border-radius: 60px;
                border: 1px solid #005b9c;
                background: #ffffff;
                padding: 16px 32px;
                margin: 8px;
                color: #005b9c;
                font-family: 'Anek Bangla', sans-serif;
                font-size: 19px;
                font-style: normal;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 100%;
                letter-spacing: 0.48px;
                margin-top: 58px;
                cursor: pointer;
              "
            >
              Hubungi Kami
            </button>
          </a>

          <!-- Primary button -->
          <a
            target="_blank"
            href="https://eku.id/profile?utm_source=brevo&utm_campaign=Ekuid - Pembayaran Bunga NEW&utm_medium=email"
            style="text-decoration: none"
          >
            <button
              style="
                border-radius: 60px;
                border: 1px solid #005b9c;
                background: #005b9c;
                padding: 16px 32px;
                margin: 8px;
                color: #fff;
                font-family: 'Anek Bangla', sans-serif;
                font-size: 19px;
                font-style: normal;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 100%;
                letter-spacing: 0.48px;
                cursor: pointer;
              "
            >
              Cek Imbal Hasil
            </button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer
      class="footer"
      style="
        background-color: #1f335b;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 34px 40px;
      "
    >
      <div
        style="
          background-color: #29406d;
          border-radius: 8px;
          padding: 27px 36px;
        "
        class="footer-wrap"
      >
        <!-- SOCIAL ICONS -->
        <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 0 4px">
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/ekuidofficial"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer noopener"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/instagram.png"
                  alt="Instagram"
                  width="40"
                  style="display: block"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
            <td style="padding: 0 4px">
              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/ekuid"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer noopener"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/linked-in.png"
                  alt="LinkedIn"
                  width="40"
                  style="display: block"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
            <td style="padding: 0 4px">
              <a
                href="https://www.tiktok.com/@ekuid"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer noopener"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/tiktok.png"
                  alt="TikTok"
                  width="40"
                  style="display: block"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <h2
          style="
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-family: 'Anek Bangla', sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 150%;
            letter-spacing: 0.306px;
            text-align: center;
          "
        >
          Download Aplikasi:
        </h2>

        <!-- DOWNLOAD BUTTONS -->
        <table
          align="center"
          cellpadding="0"
          cellspacing="0"
          border="0"
          style="margin-top: 8px"
        >
          <!-- Desktop layout -->
          <tr class="download-row-desktop" style="display: table-row">
            <td style="padding: 0 4px">
              <a
                href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ekuid/id1607289110"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/app-store-v2.png"
                  alt="Download on the App Store"
                  width="135"
                  style="display: block"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
            <td style="padding: 0 4px">
              <a
                href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ekuid.android.production"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/play-store-v2.png"
                  alt="Get it on Google Play"
                  width="135"
                  style="display: block"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Mobile stacked layout -->
          <tr class="download-row-mobile" style="display: none">
            <td style="padding: 4px 0" colspan="2">
              <a
                href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ekuid/id1607289110"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/app-store-v2.png"
                  alt="Download on the App Store"
                  width="135"
                  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="download-row-mobile" style="display: none">
            <td style="padding: 4px 0" colspan="2">
              <a
                href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ekuid.android.production"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://storage.googleapis.com/ekuid-assets/Assets/play-store-v2.png"
                  alt="Get it on Google Play"
                  width="135"
                  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto"
                  border="0"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <div
          class="disclaimer"
          style="
            background-color: #1f335b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 40px;
          "
          align="left"
        >
          <p
            style="
              color: #fff;
              font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif;
              font-size: 10px;
              font-style: normal;
              font-weight: 400;
              line-height: 150%;
              margin: 0;
            "
          >
            <strong style="font-weight: 700 !important">Perhatian:</strong>
            Ekuid adalah platform investasi dengan risiko tinggi. Pastikan kamu
            sudah memahami profil risikomu. Harap mempertimbangkan secara
            hati-hati setiap kamu melakukan investasi di Ekuid. Pastikan
            keputusan investasi kamu adalah keputusan yang kamu buat sendiri dan
            tidak ada unsur paksaan dari pihak manapun. Ekuid tidak pernah
            memaksa kamu untuk melakukan investasi di platform kami. Ekuid tidak
            bertanggung jawab atas segla bentuk risiko kerugian dan gugatan
            hukum serta hal lain yang timbul di kemudian hari.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 150%;
            letter-spacing: 0.17px;
            margin: 24px 0 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
          "
        >
          Ini adalah e-mail otomatis, mohon untuk tidak membalas e-mail ini.
        </p>

        <p
          style="
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 150%;
            letter-spacing: 0.17px;
            margin: 24px 0 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
          "
        >
          Jl. Ciniru III No.2, RT.2/RW.3, Rawa Barat, Kecamatan Kebayoran Baru,
          Jakarta Selatan 12180, Indonesia
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
